クラス MarkerBitmap

java.lang.Object
  com.erdao.maps.markerclusterer.MarkerBitmap

public class MarkerBitmap
extends Object

Utility Class to handle MarkerBitmap it handles grid offset to display on the map with offset

作成者:
Huan Erdao

フィールドの概要

フィールドの詳細

iconBmpNormal_

protected final Bitmap iconBmpNormal_
bitmap object for normal state icon

iconBmpSelect_

protected final Bitmap iconBmpSelect_
bitmap object for select state icon

iconGrid_

protected Point iconGrid_
offset grid of icon in Point. if you are using symmetric icon image, it should be half size of width&height. adjust this parameter to offset the axis of the image.

iconSize_

protected Point iconSize_
icon size in Point. x = width, y = height

itemSizeMax_

protected int itemSizeMax_
maximum item size for the marker. for the last MarkerBitmap element within list, this will be ignored.

textSize_

protected int textSize_
text size for icon

コンストラクタの詳細

MarkerBitmap

public MarkerBitmap(Bitmap src_nrm,
                    Bitmap src_sel,
                    Point grid,
                    int textSize,
                    int maxSize)
NOTE: src_nrm & src_sel must be same bitmap size.

パラメータ:
src_nrm - source Bitmap object for normal state
src_sel - source Bitmap object for select state
grid - grid point to be offset
textSize - text size for icon
maxSize - icon size threshold
